nation's 92.1 million television households tuned to a show.
   The second-place finish was CBS' best performance since the week
that ended Oct. 22.
   For the season, NBC leads with 14.9 to ABC's 13.2 and CBS' 12.3.
   Here's the top 10: ABC's ``Roseanne''; NBC's ``Cheers,'' ``The
Cosby Show,'' ``The Golden Girls,'' ``A Different World''; a
