<DATELINE>WARSAW, Poland (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   About 150 people outraged by the reported
massacre of demonstrators in Romania protested outside its embassy
here Wednesday, with some hurling stones and bottles of ink before
being stopped by police.
   Police otherwise did not hamper the protesters, who lighted
candles in the shape of a cross on the sidewalk outside the
